            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "the reason the default behavior is different is because it's typically fine to reuse the same lua version both for building and at runtime. \n\nWe do run aarch64-macos in CI but not aarch64-linux. I could try on my RPi4 with a 64-bit system to see if I can reproduce the issue there.. ",
